I was playing around with security thing right now.I am running docker images for peer and memberservices in non-dev mode.
I am using swagger UI for REST calls. I was trying registering users.
The users who are mentioned in membersrvc.yml file with affiliation are being logged in successfully. But the users like “test_vp0” are not being logged in.

And the error is:
"Error": "rpc error: code = 2 desc = \"Identity or token does not match.\""

Any hint on what is going on?

And when I tried to register myself with some name and password, It showed the following error:
"Error": "rpc error: code = 2 desc = \"Identity lookup error: sql: no rows in result set\"

any help is appreciated.
